Package: PCNR
Type: Package
Title: Protein Contact Networks in R
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "NIRJHAR BHATTACHARYYA", family = "", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nirjhar.suvo.97@gmail.com"),
    person(given = "PCNR", family = "Contributors", role = "ctb")
 )
Description: Build residue-level protein contact networks from PDB files or IDs,
    compute adjacency based on distance cutoffs, and analyze/visualize networks.
    Supports batch processing from a tabular file with columns PDB, CHAIN, ATOM, CUTOFF.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
